headline: Solar Stocks Dive As Senate Bill Keeps Cuts To Solar, Wind Energy Incentives
summary: Solar stocks such as SolarEdge and First Solar plunged Monday night after the Senate budget bill would phase out solar and wind tax credits by 2028.
